<strong>(FSG)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;A haunting novel of a woman&#8217;s lifelong witness to her father&#8217;s illness, and Stockholm’s mythic mental hospital.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>From the publisher</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="265625" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/george-saunders-heather-ann-thompson-stephen-fishbach-and-more-20-new-books-out-today/screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12-12-38-pm/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM.png" data-orig-size="962,1454" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Poor, Caleb Femi" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-198x300.png" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-678x1024.png" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-265625" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-198x300.png" alt="Poor, Caleb Femi" width="198" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-198x300.png 198w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-678x1024.png 678w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-768x1161.png 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-40x60.png 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM-33x50.png 33w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Screenshot-2026-01-15-at-12.12.38-PM.png 962w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 198px)