<strong>(MCD)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">“Caleb&#8217;s talent calls for a global stage.”<br />
<em>–</em>Virgil Abloh</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="265626" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/george-saunders-heather-ann-thompson-stephen-fishbach-and-more-20-new-books-out-today/images-1-35/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1.jpeg" data-orig-size="698,1080" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="The Great Shadow" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1-194x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1-662x1024.jpeg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-265626" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1-194x300.jpeg" alt="The Great Shadow" width="194" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1-194x300.jpeg 194w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1-662x1024.jpeg 662w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1-39x60.jpeg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1-32x50.jpeg 32w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/images-1-1.jpeg 698w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 194px) 100vw, 194px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Susan Wise Bauer, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781250272911" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Great Shadow: A History of How Sickness Shapes What We Do, Think, Believe, and Buy</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(St. Martin&#8217;s)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Eye opening, timely, and unexpectedly entertaining, <em>The Great Shadow</em> tells a vivid story about sickness and our responses to it, from ancient times until the last decade.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>Dr. Leanna Wen</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="265628" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/george-saunders-heather-ann-thompson-stephen-fishbach-and-more-20-new-books-out-today/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr.jpg" data-orig-size="1400,2125" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="A Great Act of Love" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-198x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-675x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-265628" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-198x300.jpg" alt="A Great Act of Love" width="198" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-198x300.jpg 198w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-675x1024.jpg 675w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-768x1166.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-1012x1536.jpg 1012w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/a-great-act-of-love-9781668094914_hr-1349x2048.jpg 1349w, https:/