<strong>(Summit Books)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;Sumptuous &#8230; This is a treat for historical fiction fans.&#8221;<br />
<em>–Publishers Weekly</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264381" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2026/fatima-bhutto-the-hour-of-the-wolf/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf.jpg" data-orig-size="973,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Fatima Bhutto, The Hour of the Wolf" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-195x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-664x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264381" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-195x300.jpg" alt="Fatima Bhutto, The Hour of the Wolf" width="195" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-195x300.jpg 195w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-664x1024.jpg 664w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-768x1184.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-39x60.jpg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf-32x50.jpg 32w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Fatima-Bhutto-The-Hour-of-the-Wolf.jpg 973w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 195px) 100vw, 195px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Fatima Bhutto, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/40/9781668075623" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>The Hour of the Wolf</em></a></strong><br />
<strong>(Scribner)</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8220;With otherworldly tenderness and the help of her Jack Russell terrier, Fatima Bhutto moves on from a cruel romance.&#8221;<br />
<em>–</em>Ada Calhoun</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="264375" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/lit-hubs-most-anticipated-books-of-2026/william-j-mann-black-dahlia-murder-monsters-and-madness-in-midcentury-hollywood/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/William-J.-Mann-Black-Dahlia-Murder-Monsters-and-Madness-in-Midcentury-Hollywood.jpg" data-orig-size="994,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="William J. Mann, Black Dahlia- Murder, Monsters, and Madness in Midcentury Hollywood" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/William-J.-Mann-Black-Dahlia-Murder-Monsters-and-Madness-in-Midcentury-Hollywood-199x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/William-J.-Mann-Black-Dahlia-Murder-Monsters-and-Madness-in-Midcentury-Hollywood-679x1024.jpg" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-264375" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/William-J.-Mann-Black-Dahlia-Murder-Monsters-and-Madness-in-Midcentury-Hollywood-199x300.jpg" alt="William J. Mann, Black Dahlia: Murder, Monsters, and Madness in Midcentury Hollywood" width="199" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/William-J.-Mann-Black-Dahlia-Murder-Monsters-and-Madness-in-Midcentury-Hollywood-199x300.jpg 199w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/William-J.-Mann-Black-Dahlia-Murder-Monsters-and-Madness-in-Midcentury-Hollywood-679x1024.jpg 679w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads